    "[5,[9][10][11]25]).",
    "Moreover, many variants of this model were considered and similar results were proven, see, for instance, [16,22,29,30,32].",
    "In fact, a large body of literature is devoted to diffuse-interface and Cahn-Hilliard-type models for tumor growth.",
    "Foundational modelling contributions are due to Cristini, Lowengrub, Wise and collaborators [19,20,47], of course enlightening the numerical and asymptotic investigations in [34,35].",
